snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin Mod - Zardy Foolhardy (BOT FC)
snippet.description:
Foolhardy is a stamina stream map geared towards advanced players of FNF.

Wanna see inside the development process? Check out swankys video on this: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Tgpgh_t0hY

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/xKzF7tKc6F

This mod was made in partnership with @SwankyBox, @Rozebud, StarnyArt (https://starnyart.tumblr.com/) and Myself.

Gamebanana link: https://gamebanana.com/gamefiles/17880
Alt Download: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1zpdMY6NN6YWMS__BzDZ3t1UzyoO_9z_n?usp=sharing
